{"id":232888839,"title":"【極短篇】","content":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WMVtriQkPxg\n\n承諾要伴我一生　說好的形影不離\n一場車禍帶走你　也帶走我們\n\n　山前，潑灑墨點\n　一個句點啞了我的世界\n　混濁雙眼\n　有禮地注視著雨季的間歇\n\n名字能否記憶\n撇捺是否陌生\n漆黑乘坐硯裡\n待筆起落，淚水濕了承諾\n\n患上名為沉睡的絕症\n思念是懸掛的點滴\n一點一滴推向黑影\n江山絕壁\n\n　以為到了終點就能放手\n　但到了終點，卻要如何不挽留\n\n失語是錢塘大潮\n襲向心湖邊的沙雕\n每一浪\n每一濤都是絕望的狂嘯\n\n山嵐逼近\n哭泣　在黎明前\n狂風暴雨\n\n　問那哀愁是甚麼呢\n　是在孤獨一人的床榻上留下點點淚滴\n　是在歡唱的 KTV 滑著靜默的手機\n　是在人海裡相知相遇\n　最終\n　依然不能一起走下去\n\n誰能告訴我這是什麼呢\n\n－\n歲月　你別催　該來的我不推\n　該還的還該給的我給\n歲月　你別催　走遠的我不追\n　我不過是想弄清原委","excerpt":"承諾要伴我一生　說好的形影不離，一場車禍帶走你　也帶走我們，山前，潑灑墨點，一個句點啞了我的世界，混濁雙眼，有禮地注視著雨季的間歇，名字能否記憶，撇捺是否陌生，漆黑乘坐硯裡，待筆起落，淚水濕了承諾，患","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-14T07:40:17.006Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-14T07:40:17.006Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":3,"tags":[],"topics":["極短篇","棠"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"棠","department":"nowucme","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c058f195-df34-411d-ba0b-5b224582d423","url":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/WMVtriQkPxg/hqdefault.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/WMVtriQkPxg/hqdefault.jpg","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/WMVtriQkPxg/hqdefault.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-14T07:40:17.006Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-14T07:40:17.006Z"},{"id":"c058f195-df34-411d-ba0b-5b224582d423","url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WMVtriQkPxg","normalizedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WMVtriQkPxg","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/WMVtriQkPxg/hqdefault.jpg","type":"video/youtube","tags":["ANNOTATED